title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 63] Post-Punk, Gothic, New Wave
description:
Here are four more great but obscure records from the 80's, which are astonishingly concrete albums. It's a shame so much talent was that badly overlooked. Thanks to bit torrent, these bands are being re-discovered.


Pink Turns Blue - If Two Worlds Kiss [1987]

Red Temple Spirits - If tomorrow I were leaving for Lhasa... [1989]

The Bonaparte's - ..To the Isle of Dogs [1986]

Victorian Parents - Silence Follows [1981]
